des:
Good morning, Paul. What will your first sequence of the day be? Alexa, load up Celery Man!

You can use these phrases to interact with the Cinco Identity Generator: 

Ask Celery Man to kick up the 4d3d3d3
Ask Celery Man to add sequence Oyster
Ask Celery Man to give me a print out of Oyster smiling
Ask Celery Man if we have any new sequences
Ask Celery Man if there is any way to generate a nude Tayne
Ask Celery Man if I can see a hat wobble 
Ask Celery Man if I can see a flarhgunnstow
Tell Celery Man I'm OK
Tell Celery Man we have important work to do
Tell Celery Man now Tayne I can get into
Ask Celery Man to load Celery Man
